style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Two years ago today I woke up with the worst hangover I had ever had. I had the spins, I was throwing up, and I was having a panic attack. I was about two and a half months out from losing my husband, who died very suddenly (although perhaps not entirely unexpectedly) from complications related to his substance use (alcohol). He was 37.  In 2019, it was my best friend (many, many substances). Imgur was there to support me through both losses and I am so grateful.

Nobody else has ever characterized me as an alcoholic, or said I had a problem with my drinking. Drugs? Well, that's another story. But the honest truth is that, at various times, I have had a problem with both. My spouse was a good man and a good husband. We were very in love for a very long time. And I think the best way for me to honor his life, and my own, is for me not to go down the way he did. Something will take me out eventually. But it's not going to be substance use. 

It has been two years since anything more mind altering than coffee entered my body. And I am pretty proud of that.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/xi2DxM5</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[accidie]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>more stolen memes</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/LAFkbw8</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HNjhk9n.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9MqjUeh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3ZyhTpr.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xkop2lW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wiV1Nhu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/NRpSqAq.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I like doors</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/pZSK069.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/cGMDJQu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/T3Kw1gN.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/j4E6pcu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ckF7HEE.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rTZ8kg3.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https: